data.description: Welcome to this beautifully crafted home nestled in the heart of Griffin! Built in 2018, this home offers 3 bedrooms plus a bonus room that can be used as an office or 4th bedroom. The main floor features a well-designed layout, including a 2 story foyer, a bright and airy family room, perfect for relaxation and gatherings. There's also a separate dining room, adding an elegant touch for special occasions. The eat-in kitchen is a chef's dream, offering ample counter space, modern appliances, and a cozy dining area. The primary bedroom with walk in closet and private ensuite, as well as two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom are upstairs. Enjoy the outdoors in your private fenced-in backyard. One of the standout features of this property is the absence of an HOA, offering you the freedom and flexibility to personalize your space. Welcome home!
